<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00502</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT INCREASING THE HONORARIUM AND CHRISTMAS BONUS OF BARANGAY OFFICIALS, INCLUDING BARANGAY TANODS, AND MEMBERS OF THE LUPON NG TAGAPAMAYAPA, AND GRANTING A LUMP SUM GRATUITY PAY EQUIVALENT TO ONE HUNDRED THOUSAND PESOS (P100,000.00), AND OTHER NON-MONETARY BENEFITS, AMENDING FOR THE PURPOSE SECTION 393 OF REPUBLIC ACT NO. 7160, AS AMENDED, OTHERWISE KNOWN AS THE LOCAL GOVERNMENT CODE OF 1991</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Provides retirement benefits as recognition of the barangay officials’ and workers’ contribution to the community to raise their economic and social status and by having decent, healthy and comfortable living conditions thereby encouraging them to honestly continue their public service.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>YAP, VICTOR A.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-06-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>NATURE : Reform</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Catamco (010 2016-08-15)</td><td>2. Panotes (039 2016-10-19)</td><tr><td>3. Noel (065 2017-02-01)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON LOCAL GOVERNMENT ON 2016-07-27</td></tr></table>